Package: rush
Title: Rapid Parallel and Distributed Computing
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Marc", "Becker", , "marcbecker@posteo.de", role = c("cre", "aut"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-8115-0400"))
Description: Parallel computing with a network of local and remote
    workers. Fast exchange of results between the workers through a Redis
    database. Key features include task queues, local caching, and
    sophisticated error handling.
